        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Valentine’s Day is more than a date on the calendar  it’s a celebration of togetherness, affection, and the beautiful bond you share with your wife. It’s the perfect occasion to express what words often can’t  your gratitude, admiration, and love.</p><p>If you’re searching for the perfect valentine day gift for wife, nothing compares to fine jewelry. It’s timeless, meaningful, and designed to make her feel as special as she truly is. Whether you’re newly married or have spent decades together, a diamond crafted with love is a gift she’ll treasure for years to come.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Personalised Jewelry: A Gift as Unique as She Is",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Personalised Jewelry: A Gift as Unique as She Is</h2>",
            "custom_id": "personalised",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_GUEBUp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Personalisation makes a beautiful piece of jewelry even more special. Engraved rings, name pendants, or initials on a bracelet transform a simple ornament into a memory you both cherish. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a> offers custom design options so you can add your personal touch  be it your wedding date, a meaningful word, or a heartfelt message. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Pair your customization with sustainable sparkle using<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond</span></a> jewelry ethical, brilliant, and made to last forever.</p><p>Every time she wears it, she’ll be reminded of the thought you put into choosing something truly her own.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
