        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Jewelry is more than adornment — it’s emotion turned into artistry. Here are some romantic valentine",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry is more than adornment  it’s emotion turned into artistry. Here are some romantic valentine's day gift ideas for wife that reflect different shades of love and personality.</p>",
            "custom_id": "components",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ctijNA": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1. The Charm of Rose Gold",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>1. The Charm of Rose Gold</h3><p>Warm, elegant, and feminine  rose gold embodies tenderness. A<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> makes for an exceptional valentine day special gift for wife, blending contemporary style with timeless grace. It complements both ethnic and western looks, making it a versatile piece she’ll adore.</p><h3>2. Celebrate Her Strength with a Cocktail Ring</h3><p>For the woman who lights up every room with her confidence, a bold<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/cocktail-rings-diamond\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">cocktail rings diamond</span></a> piece is the perfect choice. Its brilliance symbolizes her vibrant energy and individuality. A statement ring not only elevates her style but also reflects the strong, beautiful woman she is.</p><h3>3. Matching Couple Rings: Together, Always</h3><p>Few things are as romantic as wearing matching bands that signify your eternal bond.<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Couple rings</span></a> from Lucira capture your unity and make for a sentimental Valentine’s Day best gift for wife. Each design tells a story of two souls intertwined by love and promise.</p>",
            "custom_id": "importance",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Symbolic Jewelry with Deeper Meaning",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Symbolic Jewelry with Deeper Meaning</h2>",
            "custom_id": "symbolic",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_ry6CKN": {
