        "rich_text_AwRhRN": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry often carries emotions beyond its sparkle. Choose designs that symbolize your relationship hearts for love, infinity signs for eternity, or knots for unbreakable bonds.</p><p>A heart pendant expresses affection, an infinity bracelet stands for never-ending commitment, and a minimalist diamond band represents everlasting loyalty. Symbolic jewelry adds layers of sentiment, making your gift more than just precious metal and stones it becomes an emblem of your journey together.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
